<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Gini_coefficient&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<div class="references-small" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ul>
